<P>
   WEEKEND DUTY EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   IN ATLANTA: Chante LaGon at 404-526-5456.
</P>
<P>
   IN WASHINGTON: Rick Christie, 301-809-3419 or (cell phone)
301-910-6248.
