<P>
   Here are the stories New York Times editors are considering for
the Page 1 of Monday, Nov. 22. The N.Y. Times News Service night
supervisor is Tim Hilchey; phone: (888) 346-9867; e-mail:
hilchey(at)nytimes.com.
