Brazilians turn these days, one parliamentary commission or another
seems to be investigating official misconduct. What's more, many of
these commissions are actually yielding results. By Larry Rohter.
</P>
<P>
   CZECH-COLDWAR-MUSEUM (Prague, Czech Republic) _ The nation puts
together a living communist museum, so that the younger generation
can learn what life was like during the Cold War.
</P>
