to click away to another site to find better prices. Several
companies have developed a new breed of so-called agents _ software
tools that work with Web browser software, offering shoppers better
deals on whatever merchandise they happen to be viewing on a Web
page. (The E-Commerce Column.) By Bob Tedeschi.
